
Changelog of plasma-applet-graphicaltimetableline

0.10 - Beta 4
- The departure column in the mini timetable is now automatically sized to it's widest entry (just like the transport line column)
- Fixed train SVGs to correctly cut the train icons in the circles.

0.10 - Beta 3
- A new applet with a graphical presentation of departures, showing a street with the positions of the next departing vehicles.
- It can also show a little timetable, at the position of the stop.
- Vehicles are painted using an SVG, transport line strings are drawn if possible for local public transport.
- Completely animated (moving vehicles, departing animation).
